org.presentation.wholepresentationcontroller.impl

Class WholeExecQueueElement

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.presentation.wholepresentationcontroller.impl.WholeExecQueueElement

  • public class WholeExecQueueElement
extends Object
    This class represents immutable holder which serves as element in the queue in AsyncWholeCheckerExecutor. Either holder holds instances of objects representing page itself (content, source link and content type), or holder represents final element of the queue and holds TraversalGraph
    Author:
    radio.koza

      • WholeExecQueueElement

        public WholeExecQueueElement(TraversalGraph travGraph)
        Constructor for setting the final flag to the element. Instances representing page are set to null and traversal graph is set to not null for this element.
        Parameters:
        travGraph - Traversal graph usable for final work of wpc. May be null if not generated by web crawler.
